<div style="background:var(--panel);padding:40px;border-radius:30px;max-width:420px;text-align:center;animation:popupAppear .5s;">
<h3>D√©sactiver la maintenance ?</h3>
<p style="margin:20px 0;color:var(--muted)">Le site redeviendra accessible √† tous.</p>
